# Include guards

Do **not** use `#pragma once`. Use:

```text
__{TARGET}_{FILENAME}_H__
```

- **TARGET**: CMake 库/可执行目标名，大写（`mps_host` → `MPS_HOST`，`mps_ipc_qt` → `MPS_IPC_QT`）
- **FILENAME**: 文件名 stem 大写（`shell_window.hpp` → `SHELL_WINDOW`）；同目标下重名时加父目录
- 后缀统一 `_H__`（含 `.hpp`）
- 形如 `__…_H__`（双下划线前缀/后缀）为本仓库约定

## Target map (headers)

| Path | Target macro |
|------|----------------|
| `src/host/**` | `MPS_HOST` |
| `src/client/**` | `MPS_CLIENT` |
| `src/ipc_qt/**` | `MPS_IPC_QT` |
| `src/common/tab_strip.hpp` | `MPS_TAB_STRIP` |
| `src/common/**` (else) | `MPS_IPC` |

## Example

```cpp
// src/host/shell_window.hpp
#ifndef __MPS_HOST_SHELL_WINDOW_H__
#define __MPS_HOST_SHELL_WINDOW_H__
// ...
#endif  // __MPS_HOST_SHELL_WINDOW_H__
```

## Enforcement

Not clang-format. Follow this Cursor rule when editing headers.
